TETCH ELECTRONIC TECHNOLOGY is a professional manufacture designing and producing kinds of electronic sensor products, has 10 years of manufacturing experience. The products we produced are high speed double jet hand dryers, high speed wall-mounted hand dryers, automatic hand sterilizers, automatic soap dispensers and so on. 

We provide high quality electrical products and excellent service for hospitals, schools, food and pharmaceutical manufacturers, airports, office buildings, hotels, government agencies and research institutions and other places at home and abroad . 

We have got CCC safety certification and EU CE certification, and gained reliance and praise from clients. The atomizing hand sterilizer, which is a new and high tech product we developed, is originated with our company in China and gets the patents. This product has international standards and fills the blank of hand sterilizer domestic market. Please choose and use our products.
